00:22:23,888 --> 00:22:50,416
One of the things that has been part of the vision for Medford Square is this idea of mixed use. Mixed use could be mixed use within the same building or mixed use within the same lot. That's coming out of planning discussions and theory and practice about residential supporting the local businesses. If you get enough people living in an area,

55
00:22:50,416 --> 00:23:07,004
